      "writtenOn": "2020-10-16T19:50:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Only problem of following the testing.State to panic is that the gRPC service will exist and gRPC connection will be closed after panic. The client will not see the panic message instead it just show \n\nrpc error: code \u003d Unavailable desc \u003d transport is closing\n\nIn the new patch I did the check but just return \"false\" if it is not declared in service. \n\nDo you have any suggestion for this.",
      "parentUuid": "fdfcdf9d_2d2f5a16",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 65,
        "startChar": 23,
