      "message": "TestVars must not be exported. It essentially allows any remote test to access arbitrary variables, making checks in testing.State.Var meaningless.\n\nPlease make it unexported. Instead you can add a utility function (not a method of RPCHint) that extracts unexported vars from RPCHint. Functions defined in this package are internal to the framework (can\u0027t be imported from tests).",
